{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-template-blog-js","path":"/blog/flash_cards/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>To aid children learning language, or even adults. This is a simple phone app, that speeks the filename of an image. In the settings menu you can specify the langage to use for images in a certain folder. For example I am trying to learn the Czech language so I create a folder of images with the filenames in czech, then specify that folder to use the Czech language in the app. The Text-To-Speach engine will then read out out the Czech filename corresponding to the current image being diplayed. I even named an image the text of a short Czech nursey rhyme to help learn it.</p>\n<p><a href=\"./flash_cards_app_debug.apk\">download the Android APK</a></p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/c2a020271a687febda00cac2d7949778/21b4d/flash_card_screenshot.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 62.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Screenshot\"\n        title=\"Screenshot\"\n        src=\"/static/c2a020271a687febda00cac2d7949778/5a190/flash_card_screenshot.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/c2a020271a687febda00cac2d7949778/772e8/flash_card_screenshot.png 200w,\n/static/c2a020271a687febda00cac2d7949778/e17e5/flash_card_screenshot.png 400w,\n/static/c2a020271a687febda00cac2d7949778/5a190/flash_card_screenshot.png 800w,\n/static/c2a020271a687febda00cac2d7949778/c1b63/flash_card_screenshot.png 1200w,\n/static/c2a020271a687febda00cac2d7949778/21b4d/flash_card_screenshot.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"date":"February 28, 2020","title":"Flash Cards"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/blog/flash_cards/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"]}